dct_title_s: Αθηνα, σχεδιο ποληος, 1:7.500 = Athens, city plan, 1:7.500
dct_description_sm: General metro-area street map showing built-up/open areas and former Olympic Games venues. Shows Bus line 400 "Athens' sightseeing" Includes street index. "ChSP 270"--On cover. "ΧΣΠ 270"--On cover. "Copyright: Orama Ekdoseis." Includes text, bus-route directory, and col. ill. Text, tourist information, directories.
